Text: My, what a beautiful garden! See how the sunlight falls upon the flowers just so.
Mother must have wanted to protect this place. Why else set the silkie to guard it?
I imagine her coming here with Father, to simply sit and enjoy the tranquility.
A shelf full of cutlery, and a table made for two... This is a haven of joyful memories.
<sigh> Whilst I should like to linger still, I fear Papashan will soon note my absence. Let us be away.
Mother. Father. I will do all in my power to see this sanctuary remains unspoiled.
That jug... 'Tis not possible!
Ware the deluge of water! You will be washed away for sure!

All those puffs in a row...
You had best keep on your toes!
Is...is this a battle, or a spot of spring cleaning?

The puffs are lathered with soap now...
I fear they mean business!

I'll teach you the ways of navigation!
Mine are the waves and the winds!
Feel the might of the Navigator!
Like the stormy seas, I'm a harsh mistress!
Can you contend with she who rules the tides?
You must make an ally of the wind!
You're bloody brilliant, you are!
Rise above the whitecaps!
Boundless as the ocean!
Brace for the storm!
My trident parts the very seas!
Hahaha, well done!
You don't disappoint!
You can surely do better than that.
To seek new horizons, you must come together as one.
It falls to you and yours to navigate the seas ahead.
Come, Perykos! Thalaos!
Join us in the excitement!
Go on, my pets! Don't be shy!
I trust you don't mind if they play too.
That's the way, my clever serpents!
Go, Perykos!
A serpent after my own heart!
Swim free, my pet!
Go, Thalaos!
Yes, frolic to your heart's content!
Dance upon the waves!
Oi, cut it out, you!
Come, mortals. Make your way through our watery sanctum.
Let us see how you fare against my servants.
Only to be expected for they who vanquished my pupil Byregot.
It shall be my pleasure to welcome you personally.
Smooth sailing so far, I see. Come, then, mortals!
All hands, prepare to set sail!
Time to put to sea!
Have you got the stones to face the Navigator?
Come on, don't keep me waiting!
Let me prepare a suitable stage for our union!
After all this time, it feels strange calling to you thus.
Thank you. For making it this far.
Not long now till our journey together must end...
I shall open the way forward.
Our clash has brought us closer to our true nature.
The finishing touches, we leave to you.
You're back! The Omphalos─it suddenly transformed...
Servants!? What's the meaning of this?
Those ones, I leave to you!
It seems we're being summoned...
Go, my friend! I will stay here with the others!
So the time is come...
I am the last of us to face you.
Bask in the breath of the firmament!
Stand firm amidst the storm!
Gathering gusts, rise to the heavens!
Behold the Wanderer's arrow!
My bowstring sings!
Wind guide my arrow!
Those who hesitate are lost!
Stay not your steps!
Here our journey ends...
There!
You must persevere!
Arise!
Let all be equal!
Your prayers have given us strength.
Your prayers have given us strength. By fighting you, that strength shall be returned to the star.
Come, grant us our heart's desire!
Yes... Mankind has indeed grown strong.
You can overcome this─I know you can.
No more than I expected.
Give me cause to believe in mankind.
When this battle is over, I...
I'm glad that it was you who came to us.
Ahh, the sweet sorrow of parting...
I beg you, stay the course to the end!
Blessings be upon you on the road ahead.
May the wind ever be at your back.
Strong are they who roam!
Come, children. Fulfill our final wish.
See every last mote of us returned to the star!
By the power vested in us!
More!
Shine like the stars on high!
Mercy be upon our beloved children!
In unity lies resilience!
The only way is forward!
Overcome our final test!
In wisdom lies strength!
Fight! Fight with all your being!
Be strong, good children!
Receive of our love─and transcend it!
Ever has mankind hoped and prayed.
And those hopes and prayers have given us form.
Unto the star, we surrender our all!
Ahhh, you have truly come far...
Blessings be upon Etheirys.
Not a single mote of strength shall we hold back!
'Twas your faith that gave rise to this radiance!
The moon forms at Menphina's command!
The moon begins to wax...
Time accelerates at Althyk's command!
I have looked forward to this moment, children of man.
The Scholar shall measure your depth of knowledge.
O waters purifying, reveal their nature!
The rivers rage at my behest!
'Tis time for a test.
At what answer will you arrive, I wonder.
Seek new perspectives, and you shall find new paths.
Let flow the waters of your mind!
Prove to me the wisdom of man!
Of ignorance be cleansed!
Let us enlighten one another!
Not all knowledge is wisdom!
Share with me your ruminations.
Not all answers can be obtained through might.
Small wonder the others have exulted so.
Join me in deepest knowledge.
Well done, wise children. Well done.
Such rich, exquisite aether...
My hair shimmers with anticipation!
On your guard!
Have at you!
Fall!
Try this!
My locks are as the wind...
Supple, strong, and free!
Ah, a fair wind blows!
You feel it too, do you not?
You've done well to last this long...
But the battle has only just begun!
Ahahahaha!
I'll slaughter you all!
Dodge this if you can!
I'll make it quick!
Feel my fury!
Know your place!
You can't escape the storm!
I'll break your every bone!
Don't underestimate me!
Begone from my sight!
The insolence!
Let's try this again!
There will be nothing left of you! Nothing!
The time for play is over.
You won't leave my domain alive!
No! Do not look upon me! Leave now or...or...DIE.
Is this what became of the keyward? How dreadful...
She means to send you plummeting into the abyss. Allow me to soften your landing.
Perhaps you require more room for heroics.
Leave me to my research, or be...become...
I shall give you ground on which to fight, but you must move deftly!
She knows only destruction... I shall do my best to keep up with her rage!
Her anger is endless! It shall take time until you are under sure footing again...
Curses! We must hurry, lest they fall to their doom!
We have not lost yet. I shall lay more ground!
We must make a stand! Find your footing once more!
This is becoming routine. What crumbles, we rebuild!
Defeat Agdistis
Begone from my sight or suffer...SUFFER!
I sense convergences of aether... Beware what they may spawn!
If you will not leave... Then YOU shall become MINE!
I am...Agdistis? Yes...and this is my vessel. Have I been gifted new test subjects?
It begins again. Fear not─I shall make new ground!
I tire of this insolence. Troublesome SPECIMENS must be put down!
Defeat Hegemone
Abyssos is my charge, and I shall not shirk my duty!
Rot from the inside out.
Be swept away in a flood of aether!
Waste away.
You cannot measure against a keyward!
This is but the beginning!
Your own body betrays you!
Your time draws near. Witness true mastery before your end!
Abyssos is my domain! I shall suffer your intrusion no longer!
Protect the Holy See of Ishgard
Drive back the Dravanian Horde
Stave off Vishap's advance

Fall back and avoid Vishap's assault
Regroup with the rear guard
Defeat Vishap before the knights lose their resolve
We claim victory this day, or Ishgard falls!
Accept the Fury into your heart, and defend this bridge with your life's blood!
They mean to destroy the wards of Daniffen's Collar. Let not a single dragon pass!
Have the rear guard ready the cannons!
Everyone, fall back! Fall back now!
Do not let it reach the barrier! Hold your ground!
Remember what it is we fight for!
Fall back, and regroup! The battle is not yet lost!
We... We've lost... Ishgard will burn...
The final ward is weakened. Hurry, we must end this now!
We are the shield that keeps the Holy See! Even if it should cost us everything, they cannot be suffered to pass!
They mean to defeat us with sheer numbers, then?
Well, it's a good thing I can't count!
We must defeat their champion at all costs!
Fall back! There's nothing left to be done here.
The second ward has fallen!
The first ward has been breached!
Hold your ground! Should this barrier fall, Ishgard will be awash in flame!
Dragoons, to arms! Give the enemy no quarter!
They will know the wrath of the Azure Dragoon!
Hold nothing back!
Our enemy is not without weakness! Keep it up!
Focus your attacks on the armored dragon!
They'll need more than thick hides to prevail over us.
Damn this infernal heat!
Ishgard will not fall. Not today!
I... I cannot hold on much longer...
We will see to things here,  . Fall back and help the others guard the ward.
Yda and I have matters here well in hand.  , you must go and see to the final ward.
